{"tid":1810709,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"IGN宣佈將使用1~10整數評分","createTime":"2020-01-04T06:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T02:53:07.000Z","uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"956209ed63de7d3f8d3a7c70842cb689b69fe015","tid":1810709,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"經常關注 IGN 評分的朋友一定曾看見過那些9.3分的神作，或是被給出6.5、6.6分等差強人意的作品，但是6.5和6.6的區別在哪裡呢？也許 IGN 的編輯們自己一時也講不清楚。不過這一切都將成為歷史，IGN 已經在官方網站發佈公告，此後他們將使用1~10的整數進行評分，每個分數都準確代表著一種含義，大家以後也無需因為零點幾分的高低而產生不必要的爭論，IGN 也可以更好地通過評分與玩家進行交流。<br />\n<br />\nIGN 同時也公開了1~10不同分數所代表的的含義，簡化來看可以歸為以下標準：<br />\n10分&mdash;&mdash; Masterpiece<br />\n9分&mdash;&mdash; Amazing<br />\n8分&mdash;&mdash; Great<br />\n7分&mdash;&mdash; Good<br />\n6分&mdash;&mdash; Okay<br />\n5分&mdash;&mdash; Mediocre<br />\n4分&mdash;&mdash; Bad<br />\n3分&mdash;&mdash; Awful<br />\n2分&mdash;&mdash; Painful<br />\n1分&mdash;&mdash; Unbearable<br />\n當然，為了讓玩家們可以更加直觀地了解到每一檔評分究竟可以指代哪些遊戲，IGN 也為每檔評分選出了幾款作品，例如滿分&ldquo;10分&rdquo;就有《戰神》《最後生還者》《GTA V》《撒爾達傳說：曠野之息》4款入選。"},{"pid":"33224210f568d42a169d6fef6de579daba5e8798","tid":1810709,"uid":208227,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"咪又係一樣主觀去評分"},{"pid":"1ffb37c023ba1ec189ca679b6a403d5fb3e155a0","tid":1810709,"uid":74970,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"總之cod, pokemon 就一定9分啦"},{"pid":"aebf3db9c0ca879f12e725bc3ffe307ba767e106","tid":1810709,"uid":226155,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"1ffb37c023ba1ec189ca679b6a403d5fb3e155a0","tid":1810709,"uid":74970,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"總之cod, pokemon 就一定9分啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"Too much water"},{"pid":"145a229fdcd54793dad1bd0c0ed4337cf19430a9","tid":1810709,"uid":209333,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:46:02.000Z","msg":"ign班友識打機？<img